        </div>
        <p class="portfolio-description">
            As a trusted supplier to some of the most exclusive retailers, Yash Gems & Jewelleries (P) Ltd possesses an intimate understanding of diverse cultures and market trends. The national sales and distribution network team enables the company to cultivate close relationships with customers, providing not only products but also efficient and personalized services.
        </p>
    </div>
    <div class="image-container">
        <img src="~/Content/Image/Natural/pexels-muneeb-najar-19533158.jpg" alt="Portfolio Image 3">
